thread.title: Voting gets underway in Italy's election

title: Voting gets underway in Italy's election
text:
Voting gets underway in Italy's election 7:03am EST - 00:51 
Voting started in Italy's election on Sunday (March 4), with former prime minister Silvio Berlusconi's alliance of centre-right parties expected to win most seats but fall short of a parliamentary majority. Rough cut (no reporter narration).
